devdoc.details: Public Key Infrastructure Registry for Interbank Blockchain

returns._0: canTransfer True if authorized and within limit

isKYCValid(address).details: Check if user's KYC is valid

returns._0: isValid True if KYC is verified and not expired

recordTransfer(address,uint256).details: Record transfer usage (call from transfer contract)

registerUser(bytes).details: Register new user with PQC public key

updatePublicKey(bytes).details: Update user's PQC public key (key rotation)

verifyPQCSignature(address,bytes,bytes).details: Verify PQC signature (placeholder - actual verification off-chain via KSM)

returns._0: isValid True if signature is valid
